---
import ProductLayout from '../../layouts/ProductLayout.astro';

const title = "Oak-Framed Verandas Carlisle, Cumbria | Woodstyle Joinery";
const description = "Handcrafted oak-framed verandas in Carlisle, Cumbria. Enjoy your garden in the dry with a covered veranda built to suit your home and outdoor space.";

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What is the difference between a veranda and a porch?",
    answer: "A porch shelters your entrance door, while a veranda is a longer covered area running along the side or back of the house for sitting out and enjoying the garden. We build both, matched to your home."
  },
  {
    question: "Will a veranda keep me dry in the rain?",
    answer: "Yes. We roof our verandas to shed the weather, so you get a genuinely usable covered space rather than just shade. Add side screens and you can sit out in all but the worst of it."
  },
  {
    question: "Why choose an oak-framed veranda?",
    answer: "Oak is naturally durable and looks far better than softwood or aluminium. A well-built oak veranda ties properly into your home and adds real kerb appeal and value to your property."
  },
  {
    question: "How do I get a quote for a veranda in Carlisle or Cumbria?",
    answer: "Call us on 01228 512303 or use our contact form to arrange a free, no-obligation consultation. We will take a look at the space and prepare a design and quote to suit your home."
  }
];

const images = [
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/4741d1ea-1bf6-4233-a2e6-7df28ca0c58c.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Oak-Framed Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/7d9ce23e-ff9f-453a-9b0b-6ac497a094df.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Covered Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_0548.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Decked Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_1878.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Oak-Framed Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_3287.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Covered Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_3350.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Decked Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_3353.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Oak-Framed Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_4946.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Covered Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_6659.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Oak-Framed Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_6664.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Covered Veranda" },
  { src: "/images/products/verandas/IMG_7860.jpeg", alt: "Oak-framed veranda by Woodstyle Joinery", caption: "Decked Veranda" },
];
---

<ProductLayout {title} heading="Oak-Framed Verandas" {description} {images} {faqs}>
  <section slot="after-gallery" class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="spotlight-grid">
        <div class="spotlight-image" data-reveal>
          <img
            src="/images/products/verandas/IMG_1878.jpeg"
            alt="Oak framed veranda at Lingholm Cafe, Portinscale, Keswick"
            class="h-auto w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="spotlight-text" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
          <span class="section-kicker">Featured Project</span>
          <h2 class="mb-6 font-bold text-primary-custom heading-accent">Lingholm Cafe, Keswick</h2>
          <p class="text-xl">
            One of the best examples of our Oak Framed Verandas is situated at Lingholm Cafe, Portinscale, Keswick, CA12 5T2. This under cover eating area was created in November 2024 to provide extra capacity to the popular cafe.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="text-xl">
    <p>A veranda lets you enjoy the garden even when the Cumbrian weather isn't playing ball. It gives you a covered, sheltered spot along the back of the house to sit out, eat, or just watch the rain from the dry.</p>

    <p>We build them from solid oak framing, tied properly into the house and roofed to keep the weather off. Add lighting, a decked floor, or side screens and you've got an outdoor room you'll use far more of the year than you'd think.</p>

    <p>Whether you want somewhere shaded to sit in summer or a dry route along the back of the house, we'll build a veranda to suit. Give us a call on <strong>01228 512303</strong> to talk it over.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list mb-2">
      <li>Oak-framed verandas built to last</li>
      <li>Covered, sheltered space along your home</li>
      <li>Optional lighting, decking, and side screens</li>
      <li>Roofing that keeps the weather off</li>
      <li>Tied properly into the house and finished to complement your home</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ProductLayout>

<style>
  .spotlight-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .spotlight-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
  .spotlight-image img {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
